{"tid":2112233,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日星期五 明日大嶼有無通過？","createTime":"2020-07-17T07:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T22:40:33.000Z","uid":228962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea832095347f6d6be85c60eadb9c9957af231b2","tid":2112233,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"如題 今日係最後一日既財政年度 <br />\n香港人真係好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a25132964d28f5efeee008c1e7ebb581f9c04e","tid":2112233,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1878703e54dffbe6f9e6103cd06a28fb231bdfd","tid":2112233,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"(有直播) 明日大嶼前期研究 今日財務委員會會議議程 07-17 星期五<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2111899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2111899</a>"},{"pid":"b1607746988890130da98e85291852f5a3801276","tid":2112233,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）政府將5.5億「明日大嶼」中部水域人工島研究撥款申請，於今日的立法會財委會議程上調前。綠色和平收集逾10萬人聯署反對明日大嶼，要求立法會議員否決撥款申請，保護海洋生態。<br />\n<br />\n明日大嶼預計填海近1,700公頃，連接大嶼山、屯門及港島的交通運輸網。綠色和平資深項目主任連佩怡指，4月起發起聯署，至今已收集超過10萬人簽署反對明日大嶼計劃。連指，綠色和平曾觀察中部水域，發現該處有豐富海洋生態，包括珍貴珊瑚，國家二級級保護鳥類白腹海鵰、中華白海豚亦在該處出沒。<br />\n<br />\n連佩怡認為，市民聯署除因反對工程破壞生態，亦不滿政府於疫情下仍投放大量資源填海，而非關注民生問題。連指在目前經濟困境下，政府未有推行更多紓困、防疫政策，反而「倒錢落海」，發展一個未知前景的人工島，引起民憤。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員朱凱廸及陳志全到場接收請願信，陳志全表示會堅決反對撥款，亦提醒公眾政府堅持將撥款加入議程，反映有決心通過，「就算今日唔過，下屆都一定會再審議。」他藉此呼籲市民於立會選舉要投票予反對明日大嶼的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075578&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=efe3e2ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075578&h=9b7263cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075578</a>"},{"pid":"2286ad27477f1f03067e5313593eaea83180f5cb","tid":2112233,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"環團得得綠色和平今日有做過下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f500dfd3c0a12b4fb26061bf5895efbcd0bc04c2","tid":2112233,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2286ad27477f1f03067e5313593eaea83180f5cb","tid":2112233,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"環團得得綠色和平今日有做過下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"俾人統戰曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1753dd71e2dc99d1d6cbabb6b0d64a2336b181e9","tid":2112233,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2286ad27477f1f03067e5313593eaea83180f5cb","tid":2112233,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"環團得得綠色和平今日有做過下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:01:57.000Z","msg":"綠色和平"},{"pid":"b88a7983b86b915b1be255afdb85d1dd2e03c93d","tid":2112233,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f500dfd3c0a12b4fb26061bf5895efbcd0bc04c2","tid":2112233,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"